  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Graphite2 is a package that can be used to create "smart fonts" capable of
      displaying writing systems with various complex behaviors. A smart font
      contains not only letter shapes but also additional instructions
      indicating how to combine and position the letters in complex ways.
      Graphite2 was developed to provide the flexibility needed for minority
      languages which often need to be written according to slightly different
      rules than well-known languages that use the same script.
    </para>

